      "comment": "DOCHERTY (1) has good early dash but last time was shuffled out the back and missed the frame, finishing seventh (26.58) in a Special conditions H at Warragul. Placed the start prior (26.58) at Warragul after firing out of the boxes. Form at the trip sound including eight wins. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Can bounce back. PAW BRODY (2) stalked the lead from a low draw and fought on well to finish 2.25 lengths back in second (24.11) at Bendigo in a Grade 5 over 425m. Must be included in calculations. SCOTT CHARISMA (6) is rarely out of the finish, recording 18 places from 38 starts. Has been in the minors the last two runs, the latest finishing third (24.18) at Bendigo. Has a good record at this journey. Winning chance.",
